Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.77,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,470)}Flower of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:21.85,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:33.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,A week from now, we'll launch \Nfireworks from the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:36.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.82,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You need help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.17,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Here are some phone books.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.78,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:18.20,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might need more \Nthan just Kiriyako City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.72,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to use the phone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.18,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.60,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.92,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there was nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.57,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,that I could do about Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.16,Fireworks,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:57.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.17,Glooge,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hokkaido pyrotechnicians
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please make an exception?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:09.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.78,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:14.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:24.61,Board,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}{\fs18}Hanazawa Chamber of Commerce\NKumano City Community Union\NYamagishi Corporation\NMinami-machi Ltd.\NSawamura Fireworks Group\NKabato-ya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:24.61,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here while \Nyou're making others do your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.32,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:28.67,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.25,notebook,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1229)}Firework technicians\N* Budget\N* Labor\NCity permission\N* Contact City Hall\N* Ask Tourism Union for assistance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.29,Closed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.17,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.20,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.02,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give \Nup partway anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.59,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.95,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we get permission \Nfor the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.69,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, the bath's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.41,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, she's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.08,Saucer,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No Saucer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.91,Fireworks2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Fireworks Set
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.78,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.87,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.72,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.90,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.78,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.19,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:52.48,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:55.35,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.03,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sou—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:00.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Be quick if you want to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.84,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy, unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.16,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.18,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're never going to \Nget rid of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.98,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya was desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:12.89,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.42,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to launch fireworks \Neven though it's futile...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.56,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She even has Koharu involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.64,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.59,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:28.94,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.81,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You've been angry at me, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.87,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Because I didn't listen to you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.62,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.38,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:43.50,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:46.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing? \NStupid Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.49,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.26,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.65,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'll be tough while \Nthe saucer is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:15.16,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.62,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.65,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Salisbury steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:26.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:29.92,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.01,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We get to see fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.85,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If we get permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.68,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.89,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.89,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What're fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.04,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.03,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:56.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks go up high in \Nthe sky, and go like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.95,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.60,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Pssh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Those are fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, from the festival \Nseven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,They had fireworks at the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,They're so sparkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.18,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:25.21,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Pssh! Boom! Crackle, crackle, crackle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:32.71,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:36.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,if you want, I'll lend you my album.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.33,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:42.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.68,sora-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Koharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.34,sora-main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.34,storage,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Storage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.10,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.01,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I still had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.27,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.97,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make fireworks \Nhappen in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.53,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.87,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.03,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:04.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You just made that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.79,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,So what about fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:11.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I would be happy if \Nyou could launch fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I wanted you to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,With the same people as back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:29.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:33.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.40,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.10,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.28,sora-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:11.00,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.78,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.21,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.48,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.04,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.49,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:32.50,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's tomorrow, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming, too, Togawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:39.96,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.88,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,If the fireworks are happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.30,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.24,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:22.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd \Never talk to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:24.47,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you're hanging \Nout with Nonoka now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:31.77,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,No, all of us have been \Ntogether since way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.80,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka doesn't know what \Nhappened seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yet she wants to launch fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:49.91,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Nonoka thought \Nwhat you were doing was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What did you actually \Nwant to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.22,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.09,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Nonoka would make me some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.09,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.52,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What's your relationship with Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:18.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.03,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you where \Nand when you met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,She taught me a song on a snowy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.28,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.73,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:29.98,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:36.96,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dodge my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:41.97,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it hasn't snowed since \NNonoka came back to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.90,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You're good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.93,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you friends anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.35,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Because Nonoka is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:57.96,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,A huge liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:05.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You'll smile if you eat delicious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.88,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.49,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.41,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you go off without telling \Nanyone in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.33,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No reason, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.46,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I just got myself hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.45,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.82,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.52,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.39,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was because of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.96,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.60,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.21,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.93,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm acting this way, \Neven though you're helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.41,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:30.20,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should finish \Ndoing what you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.42,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.96,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here with a different request today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.13,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.16,sora-flashback,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:21.62,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise to my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.67,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,to meet my them at the pier \Nwhen the fireworks start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.36,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I can go, right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.99,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,All right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.72,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.42,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:39.76,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.15,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, the shop's \Ngoing to be busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.68,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go off to the \Nfestival by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.88,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:01.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.69,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:06.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:07.94,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:08.92,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Switch spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.24,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:15.24,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, \NI don't know about Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.72,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.82,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.42,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.16,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.23,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.98,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.65,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks aren't even happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.50,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.33,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy when you're all smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:10.02,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:13.28,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka's smiling lots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.79,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.93,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.55,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:47.43,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Am I smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.24,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:04.45,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.06,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.97,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:31.69,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\a6}Fall Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:29.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This poster's from way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:11.94,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:24.70,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yuzuki, we couldn't do fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:30.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, you shouldn't be apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:36.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:39.41,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:44.22,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,To you, to Koharu, and to Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:49.22,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:54.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:06.74,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So all we have are these \Nsparklers that I brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:12.85,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Mine soaked up a ton of \Nmoisture over the past seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.12,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:19.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad Togawa-san isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.10,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sparklers are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.65,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Pssh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:25.65,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.93,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:58.47,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:36.35,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial \NMethod{\i0}: "True Friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:37.68,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:41.19,sora-next-ep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,True Friends
